	"Mortal Kombat is a game that needs no introduction. This is the game that made parents worry about the media, and probably caused all that video games make people violent stuff. I chose to run the Genesis version because it's the one I played a lot when I was younger. I was initially going to play as Rayden, but I chose Johnny Cage instead.
	$LF
]div
